# Keep the build context small and the image clean.
# The Rust builder stage compiles fresh binaries, so any host build artifacts
# are noise (and a local runtime/target can be hundreds of MB).
**/target/
runtime/target/
**/node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
.git/
**/*.docx
docs-site/
.arves-registry/
.claude/
